      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Chapter 1


    We were married for about five, six years.

    Of course
    we weren''t happy, but who was?


    Economy took a hit after AmethystCorps
    bubble broke,

    Jobs are scarce, homelessness is on the rise.

    We were
    home more often than not, without any money.


    I remember the day it all
    ended like it was yesterday...'
